{"tid":411324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我愛加菲貓管理員深水埗撞車死咗！！！！","createTime":"2017-09-23T16:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T20:12:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":45,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"202b5907efe9326dc3b8b3364d13a17479d89737","tid":411324,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:45:03.000Z","msg":"各位貓友，由於另一管理員加創立加菲貓群組既版主，因昨晚深水埗車禍走左了，我希望大家呢幾日唔好post加菲貓，以示對群主既懷念。聲爺，早兩日仲同你傾緊計，估唔到今日收到呢個令人痛心既消息，祝你一路好走！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/ilovegarfield/permalink/10155866382384916/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Filovegarfield%2Fpermalink%2F10155866382384916%2F&d=PHGfPT%2BmP5xnPm26GZDJMJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2730bd85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/ilovegarfield/permalink/10155866382384916/</a>"},{"pid":"e8e0a53ab6273c570f045fc47a5c1b709b524135","tid":411324,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"好慘，rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977deb5f0a0a7fa3c363703fc0914a78cbb38316","tid":411324,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbe219741b2571e31d1c2a53a41b4693f8b4721","tid":411324,"uid":116530,"like":12,"dislike":288,"score":-276,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:52:36.000Z","msg":"養貓養到你咁開心呀喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650ccc3dd60928f66f4cd1bbcbcf730ecfe7ff31","tid":411324,"uid":21423,"like":16,"dislike":102,"score":-86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:58:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a4a1cbd0479b918d744aeef16ff277b8dca187d","tid":411324,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":29,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d02ec599d09c1f15901e51af41b5e2af01d9a484","tid":411324,"uid":82917,"like":136,"dislike":13,"score":123,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:01:50.000Z","msg":"連登啲人真係好撚口賤"},{"pid":"8e35855659f4667ecb3b96f44827a57ffa83d075","tid":411324,"uid":56878,"like":121,"dislike":4,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登啲人真係好撚口賤</blockquote><br />\n口賤到以為有印花拎可以換煲"},{"pid":"9d471f7492a1fb38e0b1e301bb3e1a6654e762e6","tid":411324,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:04:40.000Z","msg":"奪命車禍：同捲車底夫死妻傷　友人悼念聲爺<br />\n09月23日(六) 22:48更新 16:22建立   <br />\n<br />\n好友於fb發文悼念聲爺。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n車禍中喪生車底的男死者王友聲(49歲)，人稱「聲爺」，友人得悉他在事件中喪生，今午到其Facebook發文悼念，並指「You are always my best friend. I will miss you forever (你永遠是我的好友，會永遠懷念你)」。 <br />\n<br />\n從聲爺的Facebook可見，他與妻子居於元朗錦田橫台山村屋，他畢業於珠海學院資訊科學系，之後曾執教鞭，2008年起與弟妹在大角咀開設泰國餐館，不過他甚少落舖頭幫手。夫妻二人都是愛貓人士，家中至少飼養了3隻貓咪，他不時上載與貓兒的生活照，惹來不少朋友留言讚好。聲爺生前愛航拍，又對UFO(不明飛行物體)有研究，是香港飛碟學會IT組組長。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，他們亦經常四出品嚐美食，Facebook上滿是美食照片，友人不時留言表示食指大動。出事前一晚，他還透露「老婆放假整幾味，今晚我有食神啦」，並上載數張佳餚照片，詎料昨晚竟生意外。據悉，黃與妻子膝下猶虛，昨晚兩人拍拖外出，不料雙雙慘被捲入巴士車底，夫死妻傷，從此陰陽相隔。 <br />\n<br />\n鄰居透露，聲爺夫婦幾個月前搬至，雖然彼此交流不多，但覺得2人友善有禮，會主動點頭打招呼。2人平日很早便離家，聲爺通常於傍晚6時許下班回家，而其妻則較晚。"},{"pid":"33dcb90ac925259a26d85524714ac3c6b80ebc0f","tid":411324,"uid":113773,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:06:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養貓養到你咁開心呀喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆你個街手殘禁錯正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1eb9ddf714ee02012ab4bab1da8f9f310ff855e","tid":411324,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:16:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170923/mobile/bkn-20170923162213823-0923_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170923%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170923162213823-0923_00822_